&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Active Security Clearance at the Secret or Top Secret (TS/SCI preferred) level&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong leadership experience with open architecture or software development teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Current defense open architectures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Large scale systems integration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Software team leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;System-of-systems integration and deployment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us and be part of a team that&#39;s making an impact at the forefront of technology and innovation. While

